cast.overview: One man's campaign for vengeance takes on national stakes after he is revealed to be a former operative of a powerful and clandestine organization known as Beekeepers.
cast.title: The Beekeeper

cast.overview: A cold and mysterious new security guard for a Los Angeles cash truck company surprises his co-workers when he unleashes precision skills during a heist. The crew is left wondering who he is and where he came from. Soon, the marksman's ultimate motive becomes clear as he takes dramatic and irrevocable steps to settle a score.
cast.title: Wrath of Man

cast.overview: The Blind Man has been hiding out for several years in an isolated cabin and has taken in and raised a young girl orphaned from a devastating house fire. Their quiet life together is shattered when a group of criminals kidnap the girl, forcing the Blind Man to leave his safe haven to save her.
cast.title: Don't Breathe 2

details.biography:
Rocci - Boy Williams was born November, 1978 in Basingstoke. Always eager to keep the room entertained, Rocci was keen on Acting from a young age.

After a number of years as a professional mixed martial artist Rocci decided to follow his dreams of acting and landed his first Role in Angel has fallen acting opposite Gerard Butler. Soon after he was cast alongside Jason Statham in Guy Ritchies Wrath of man.

In the sequel to Don't Breath Rocci was able to utilise his background in MMA (and not to mention he is a black belt in Brazilian Jiu JItsu) in one of the most brutal fight sequences on screen. "Performing all of my own stunts added to the realism of the fight scene" ~ Rocci Williams.
details.name: Rocci Williams
